of villages to force assimilation <ORGANIZATION> MTI </ORGANIZATION> reported June 20 that <LOCATION> Romania </LOCATION> had completed a barbed wire fence 6 -LCB- feet to 8 \ feet high along 90 percent of the countries' common A subsequent <ORGANIZATION> MTI </ORGANIZATION> report said Romanian authorities had piled sand on roads leading to the border, apparently to block traffic, and border guards had noticed a kind of steel `` car trap.'' <ORGANIZATION> MTI </ORGANIZATION> said <LOCATION> Romania </LOCATION> started building the fence 1 -LCB- years ago, but the pace of construction was speeded up in March.
