elopments prior to next week's <ORGANIZATION> Warsaw </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Pact </ORGANIZATION> summit in <LOCATION> Bucharest </LOCATION>, which will draw the <LOCATION> East </LOCATION> bloc's party general secretaries, including Soviet leader <PERSON> Mikhail </PERSON> <PERSON> S. </PERSON> <PERSON> Gorbachev </PERSON>.
