ecause he was suspended from <ORGANIZATION> ODU </ORGANIZATION> in 1984 for biting a female student on the neck, <PERSON> Souther </PERSON> was turned down for officer candidate school in the <ORGANIZATION> Navy </ORGANIZATION>. `` He was very bitter about what happened to him as far as the problem on campus,'' <PERSON> Fahey </PERSON> said. `` He really wanted to become a naval officer.''
