es. <ORGANIZATION> Allegis </ORGANIZATION> sold its non-airline companies and renamed itself <ORGANIZATION> UAL </ORGANIZATION>, which was its title before it acquired those businesses and renamed itself <ORGANIZATION> Allegis </ORGANIZATION>.
