5.11 an ounce. Silver prices were unchanged. On <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION>'s Comex, silver bullion for current delivery settled at $ 5.306 a troy ounce, the same as late Monday. Silver closed in <LOCATION> London </LOCATION> at $ 5.33 an ounce, also unchanged from Monday.
